<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-146852" number="39569" version="2741">
			<HEADING>Chapter 21: Petitions for Rulemaking</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17398" name="T16C021"/>Chapter 21: Petitions for Rulemaking</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131485" number="39570" version="2169">
								<HEADING>§ 21-01 Purpose.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17400" name="T16C021_21-01"/>§ 21-01 Purpose.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131484" number="39571" version="2497">
									<PARA>These Rules govern the procedures by which members of the public may submit to the Department Petitions for Rulemaking pursuant to § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1043" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1043</LINK>(g) of the New York City Charter (City Administrative Procedures Act) and the procedures for the Department&apos;s consideration and disposition of such Petitions. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131483" number="39572" version="2169">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/20/2021, eff. 1/19/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131488" number="39573" version="2169">
								<HEADING>§ 21-02 Definitions</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17402" name="T16C021_21-02"/>§ 21-02 Definitions</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131482" number="39574" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Department.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Department&quot; means the Department of Sanitation. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131481" number="39575" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Person.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Person&quot; means an individual, partnership, corporation or other legal entity, and any individual or entity acting in a fiduciary or representative capacity. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131480" number="39576" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petition.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petition&quot; means a request or application for the Department to adopt a Rule. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131479" number="39577" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petitioner.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petitioner&quot; means the person who files a Petition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131478" number="39578" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Rule.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Rule&quot; has the same meaning as in § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1041" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1041</LINK>(5) of the New York City Charter. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131477" number="39579" version="2169">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/20/2021, eff. 1/19/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131487" number="39580" version="2169">
								<HEADING>§ 21-03 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17404" name="T16C021_21-03"/>§ 21-03 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131476" number="39581" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any Person may submit a Petition to consider the adoption of a Rule. The Petition must include: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131475" number="39582" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Rule to be considered, with proposed language for adoption; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131474" number="39583" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitioner&apos;s arguments in support of adoption of the Rule; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131473" number="39584" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The name, address, telephone number, and email address of the Petitioner or his or her authorized representative; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131472" number="39585" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(4)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The signature of Petitioner or his or her representative. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131471" number="39586" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Petition must be submitted by mail to New York City Department of Sanitation, Bureau of Legal Affairs, 125 Worth Street, Room 710, New York, NY 10013 or by electronic mail to rulepetitions@dsny.nyc.gov. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131470" number="39587" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any change in the name, address or telephone number of the Petitioner or his or her authorized representative must be reported to the office of which the Petition was submitted. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131469" number="39588" version="2169">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/20/2021, eff. 1/19/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131486" number="39589" version="2169">
								<HEADING>§ 21-04 Procedures for Consideration and Responses to Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17406" name="T16C021_21-04"/>§ 21-04 Procedures for Consideration and Responses to Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131468" number="39590" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>When a Petition submitted in proper form is received, the Department will: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131467" number="39591" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Register receipt of the Petition with the date it was received and assign the Petition a number or other unique identifier. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131466" number="39592" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Deny or approve the Petition within 60 days from the date the Petition was received. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131465" number="39593" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(A)<TAB tab-count="1"/>If such petition is denied, the Department will deny such Petition in a written statement containing the reasons for denial. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131464" number="39594" version="2169">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(B)<TAB tab-count="1"/>If such petition is granted, the Department will state in writing the intention to grant the Petition and to initiate Rulemaking by a specified date. The Department is not required to grant the entirety of a Petition or to follow the wording of a petition that has been granted. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131462" number="39595" version="2770">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 12/20/2021, eff. 1/19/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-068]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>